to start a git repo
  - git init (to create the .git folder conatine all info and config for git repo)

  - git status to view our files status

  - .gitignore file

  - git add .

   -git remote add origin git@github.com:Tidjini/node-todo-api.git

   -git push -u origin master


   Mongoose is an ORM (Object Relational Mapping) for mongodb
